{
  "chapter": 61,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十一回 阴狠毒辣：十大恶人重聚荒宅，杜杀逼问欧阳兄弟藏宝下落。欧阳丁谎称宝藏在龟山，画下假地图。阴九幽赶到，透露远远瞧见燕南天骑马而至，众恶人闻风丧胆纷纷逃离。屠娇娇剁下欧阳兄弟手足，浇上白糖，手段残忍。小鱼儿救下欧阳兄弟，欧阳丁临死前说出真相：龟山有恶魔埋伏，真正的宝藏在汉口城八宝里。欧阳兄弟临终忏悔，求小鱼儿用宝藏赎罪。小鱼儿深受触动，独自洗漱换衣，到状元楼用餐，目睹花无缺与江别鹤的声势，最终决心不再躲避，直面宿命。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "杜大叔，你好么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "text": "你还认得我么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "小……小弟怎敢不……不认得杜老大？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "腿不能动，用手爬下来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "小……小弟腿已不能动了，怎么下去？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你还不快过去见见你的李大叔，这些年来，他天天在想着你哩，只不过不知道他是不是想吃你的肉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "看样子，李大叔莫非在生气么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "李大叔，你可莫要真的生气，人一生气，肉就会变酸的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不想你这小鬼倒还记得这句话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二十年来，咱们兄弟还是第一次聚了这么多，当真是盛会难逢，不可不好生庆祝庆祝。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中若有人知道咱们这班老伙伴又聚在一起了，不知该如何想法？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们只怕连苦胆都要吓破。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苦胆千万不可吓破，否则肉就苦得不能吃了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，只差阴老九了，不知他遇见了什么事，怎地还未赶来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟瞧见诸兄又复重聚，实是不胜之喜。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这实在该喝两杯庆祝庆祝才是。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "是呀，但咱们的钱已被你骗光了，哪里还有钱买酒。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "屠大姐只要放了小弟，小弟必定立刻去找那姓路的，拼了命也要将那批东西抢回来。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "东西在哪里？说！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "真……真被路仲达……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "你明知要说的，为何不早说，难道非要人家用这种法子对付你不可？这也就怪不得别人心狠手辣了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "东西既在，在哪里？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "我说出之后，你们还要杀我么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "哈哈，咱们本是如弟兄一样，怎会杀你们？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "这话要杜老大说，我兄弟才放心。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "你说出之后，我等绝不伤你性命！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "那批东西就藏在龟山之巅的一个洞穴里……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟还可为诸兄画一幅详细的地图。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "此图还是交给杜老大保管，否则我绝不放心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，除了杜老大外，我也是谁都不放心的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "哈哈，阴老九果然是聪明人，等咱们费了半天力后，他才来抢便宜。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "你们费了力，难道我没有？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "你费了什么力？难道被鬼缠住脱不了身？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正是遇见鬼了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你猜是什么鬼？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "能缠住你的鬼，倒也少有，但能令你害怕的人，倒有一个……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "你莫非遇见了燕南天？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若遇上他，还能来么？……我只不过远远瞧见他了，瞧见他骑在马上，生龙活虎，比以前好像还要精神得多。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "他……他是往哪里去的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎知他要到哪里去？说不定是往这里来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的确不是久留之地，咱们走吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走自然要走，谁不走我佩服他。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "求求你们，将我也带走吧，我……我也不愿见着燕南天。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你……你干脆给我个痛快，杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "text": "杜老大说过不杀你，我怎能杀你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你……你好狠的心，好毒的手段！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "你现在虽然这么说，但我若落在你手上，你只怕比我还要狠上十倍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "求求你，赏我一刀吧，我死也感激你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "我突然变得慈悲起来了，你们奇怪么？我虽然知道你们都不是好东西，但要你们这样慢慢的死，却也未免太过分了些。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你若肯救我，我……必定重重报答你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "只要你能活下去，我一定救你，但我不要你什么报答。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那批宝物并非藏在龟山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我在那种情况下说出来的话，任何人都不会以为是假的了，是么？我正是要他们认为如此，否则那些恶鬼又怎会上我的当！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "他们最多也不过空跑一趟而已，也算不得是上当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我兄弟要他们上当，岂只空跑一趟而已。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这一趟他们纵能活着回来，至少却也得将半条命留在龟山上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我兄弟告诉他们的那个地方，没有藏宝，却有个恶魔。这恶魔已有许多年未露面了，他们做梦也不会想到他会藏在龟山。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "咱们就算死了，但他们也没有好受的，遇见了这恶魔，他们身受之惨，只怕比咱们还惨十倍。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "你们既已要死了，何苦要害人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我明知他们反正是放不过我的，索性多吃些苦，多受些罪，把他们也拖下水，我欧阳丁正是拼命也要占便宜的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我兄弟两条命，要换他们五条命，这买卖做得连本带利都有了，我欧阳当正是宁死也不吃亏。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "你们这简直不是明知必死才害人的，简直是为了害人，而宁可去死，像你们这样的人，倒也少见得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "告诉你，那真的藏宝之处，是在……汉口城，八宝里，巷子到头右面的三栋小屋子里，那门是黄色的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们都以为咱们必定也将财宝藏在什么荒无人迹的秘密山洞里，却不想咱们偏偏要将财宝藏在人烟稠密之处，叫他们做梦也想不到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "text": "很好，现在你们若要去作恶鬼，只管去作吧，但你们却莫要忘了，作恶鬼是要上刀山、下油锅的，那滋味并不好受。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我不是恶人……也不愿意做恶鬼，我……我不愿下地狱。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "text": "你现在才想起说这话，不嫌太迟了么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_dang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳当",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "求求你，用我们的财宝，去为我们做些好事吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳丁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错不错，我们坏事做的太多了，求求你为我们赎赎罪吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "奇怪，很多人都以为用两个臭钱就可以赎罪，这想法岂非太可笑了么？若是真的如此，天堂上岂非都是有钱人，穷人难道都要下地狱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ding",
      "text": "但无论如何，我总会为你们试试的，你们现在才知道忏悔，虽已迟了，但总比死也不肯忏悔好一点，你们只管放心死吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "欧阳兄弟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "求求你，帮个忙吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "酒楼客人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳兄弟今天晚上想必还是要到这状元楼来的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "欧阳兄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承蒙江大侠瞧得起，倒也发给俺一张帖子，今天晚上正是少不得还要到这里来喝上一顿。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "酒楼客人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江大侠今天晚上请客，正是要为花公子庆功，花公子此刻却怎地要走了？难道他竟不给江大侠面子。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "酒楼客人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天风和日丽，天色晴朗，花公子想必正是带着他未来的妻子出城去踏青，绝不会是真要走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "酒楼众人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子你好！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这样躲着他，究竟要躲到几时，我难道真的一辈子都躲着他么……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    }
